headline: 2 Reasons to Like PCAR and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Over the past six months, PACCAR’s shares (currently trading at $88.17) have posted a disappointing 19.9% loss while the S&P 500 was down 10%. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
